01:39:32.360 --> 01:39:33.560
And that's the difference.

01:39:33.560 --> 01:39:34.760
Now, let me put it this way.

01:39:34.760 --> 01:39:37.240
So it's really sharp in your minds.

01:39:37.240 --> 01:39:42.040
